defaultI would say it is a generally good thing.  It is not necessarily easy, but it certainly brings additional knowledge to the university, and one would hope it would bring the latest thinking into industry.  One sees that promoted in bigger industries.  BAE Systems, Rolls
default&#x2011;
defaultRoyce, etc., have relatively well
